		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		/*margin: auto;*/
		overflow: auto;
		background-color: rgba(0,0,0);
		background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
		padding-top: 60px;
	}
	.modal-content{
		width: 30%;
		height: auto;
		margin: 5% auto 15% auto;
		border: 1px solid #888;
		background-color: #fefefe;
	}
	/* styling for login form ends */
</style>
